    <h1>Apple Business Connect</h1>
    <p class="description">Apple's free platform for managing how a business appears across <strong>Apple Maps, Siri, Spotlight, Safari, and Wallet</strong>. Launched January 2023. With over 1 billion active Apple devices and <strong>5+ billion Apple Maps requests per week</strong>, ignoring it means invisibility to a big share of mobile searchers.</p>
