            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Sign in at business.apple.com with an Apple ID, search for your business, and claim it. Apple supports verification by phone, email, or document upload. Multi-location businesses can claim all locations through a single Apple ID.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

